            <h3 class="major">Welcome</h3>
            <p>Welcome to Taste on Wheels, your ultimate destination for discovering and experiencing a diverse array of
            culinary delights on wheels! We are dedicated to connecting food truck enthusiasts with their favorite
            mobile eateries while offering food truck owners a platform to showcase their unique offerings.</p>

            <h3 class="major">Our Features</h3>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Food Truck Listings:</strong> Owners can post their trucks with details like hours, cuisines, and offers.</li>
              <li><strong>Owner Dashboard:</strong> Manage listings easily via a dedicated dashboard.</li>
              <li><strong>Interactive Ratings:</strong> Customers can leave feedback and reviews.</li>
              <li><strong>Get Directions:</strong> Built-in Google Maps navigation to trucks.</li>
              <li><strong>Tailored Recommendations:</strong> BOGO and top-rated trucks on the homepage.</li>
              <li><strong>Efficient Search:</strong> Easily find trucks by cuisine, dish, or location.</li>
            </ul>

