              <li><strong>Packages:</strong> express-session, connect-mongodb-session, cookie-parser, connect-flash, express-validator, multer, etc.</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 class="major">Join Our Culinary Journey</h3>
            <p>Whether you're a food truck enthusiast eager to explore new tastes or a passionate owner looking to reach a
